texts.text: This article is about the history of the signs.png-atlas file. For a comprehensive history of block texture changes, see Java Edition history of textures.
signs.png-atlas is a procedurally-generated texture atlas used to store textures for all signs.

signs.png-atlas is a fixed-width 256 × 128-pixel file that store textures for all signs. It includes: entity/signs/acacia.png, entity/signs/birch.png, entity/signs/crimson.png, entity/signs/dark_oak.png, entity/signs/jungle.png, entity/signs/oak.png, entity/signs/spruce.png, entity/signs/warped.png.
